Hey Radhika! I hope you're doing fantastic! Firstly, I genuinely, genuinely apologize for using Outlook to ask you out! I'm incredibly sorry if you feel offended. That is not at all my intention. My only intention here is to make a great friend today. All that I ask is that I have is that you are done with your NLP assignments on time, you have a full set of 32 teeth, and don't make strange noises when you are stressed. Looking forward to hearing back from you 🙂
